@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_siexez(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.55 / v1 + 0.12)) / ((v1 + 0.60 + tmp + 0.51) * (tmp + 0.37 + tmp + 0.90)))
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.64 / v1 + 0.30)) + wp.exp((tmp + 0.59 * v2 + 0.59)))
    v2 = (0.00 - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.15) - (v0 + 0.54 / v1 + 0.50)))
    v0 = wp.cos(0.62)
    v2 = v2
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
